    <item>
      <title>啤酒禁令导致赞比亚重新开放刚果边境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/zambia-reopens-congo-border-after-beer-ban-led-to-closure</link>
      <description><![CDATA[赞比亚周二恢复与刚果民主共和国的贸易，此前两国官员举行会谈解决贸易争端，该争端导致卢萨卡关闭两国边境，阻止了世界第二大铜生产国的出口。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/zambia-reopens-congo-border-after-beer-ban-led-to-closure</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 09:22:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管中国人民银行放宽政策，但中国信贷增长仍弱于预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/china-s-credit-growth-weaker-than-expected-despite-pboc-easing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[7月份，尽管中央政府采取了货币宽松措施，但中国的信贷扩张速度低于预期，而7月份通常是融资活动的淡季。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/china-s-credit-growth-weaker-than-expected-despite-pboc-easing</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 09:10:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国投资者信心跌至 1 月以来最低水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/german-investor-confidence-plunges-to-lowest-since-january</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于一系列令人失望的数据和近期全球股市的动荡，投资者对德国经济的信心跌至一月份以来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/german-investor-confidence-plunges-to-lowest-since-january</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 09:07:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Just Group 业绩远超预期 股价飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/just-group-soars-as-results-blow-guidance-out-of-the-water</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于退休产品需求旺盛，Just Group Plc 继续受益于更高的利率，因此该公司上调了今年的业绩预期，其股价周二飙升至六年来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/just-group-soars-as-results-blow-guidance-out-of-the-water</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 09:04:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>IEA 数据显示，如果 OPEC+ 增加供应，石油过剩将迫在眉睫</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/oil-market-faces-surplus-if-opec-boosts-supply-iea-data-shows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际能源署的数据显示，如果 OPEC+ 继续执行增加供应的计划，全球石油市场下个季度将从短缺转为过剩。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/oil-market-faces-surplus-if-opec-boosts-supply-iea-data-shows</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 08:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
