    <item>
      <title>东京削减债券销售计划 反映利率紧张情绪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/tokyo-cuts-bond-issuance-plan-in-sign-of-interest-rate-jitters</link>
      <description><![CDATA[东京都政府计划本财年削减债券销售，这再次表明日本信贷市场正准备应对央行加息后投资者对债务的需求减弱。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/tokyo-cuts-bond-issuance-plan-in-sign-of-interest-rate-jitters</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 06:56:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>软银支持的 Brainbees 在孟买交易首日飙升 52%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/baby-products-retailer-firstcry-s-parent-set-to-debut-in-india-listing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[婴儿用品零售商 Brainbees Solutions Ltd. 的股价在上市首日大幅上涨，因为该公司相对于同行而言估值较低，吸引了新兴新股销售市场的投资者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-13/baby-products-retailer-firstcry-s-parent-set-to-debut-in-india-listing</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 13 Aug 2024 01:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>受中东紧张局势和 OPEC 关注，油价五连涨终结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-13</link>
      <description><![CDATA[油价在连续五天上涨后下跌，中东冲突可能升级，但国际能源署预计，如果 OPEC+ 在下个季度按计划增加产量，将会出现盈余，从而抵消油价上涨的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-aug-13</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 23:25:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
